    Factor comparison

    factor_comparison.Rd

    Compute anova and fit index to compare multiple factor analyse fit for multiple factors solution

    factor_comparison(data, items, factors)

    Arguments

    data

    a data.frame containing the test or scale response in columns

    items

    The name of the items

    factors

    a facto class object from factor_explorer() or a vector with the number of factor

    Value

    a table with a CHI² comparison and CFI, TLI, RMSEA and SRMR differences

    Examples

    data("inference")
items <- c(paste0("item_0",3:9),"item_10")
f <- factor_explorer(inference, items)
factor_comparison(inference, items, f)
